cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG

Reasoning: 
1) cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on facial emotion recognition and the analysis of different face regions. 
2) cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also likely as the paper discusses the importance of facial emotion recognition in the field of human-machine interaction. 
3) cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with analyzing emotions in real-world conditions, which involves multimedia data. 
4) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques for emotion recognition. 
5) cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category as the paper focuses on the classification accuracy and the contribution of different face areas to different emotions through experimental analysis.
